When this happens and it's funny,

157
00:11:03,219 --> 00:11:05,200
it breaks the immersion, it breaks the game.

158
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:07,941
So it doesn't add to the gameplay experience.

159
00:11:07,941 --> 00:11:08,941
So it has to be a no.

160
00:11:08,941 --> 00:11:12,742
Last year, we released

161
00:11:12,742 --> 00:11:14,803
a new feature to our game called the Archives.

